{"tid":164154,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"關於去福岡加鹿兒島嘅問題","createTime":"2017-03-20T13:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T02:44:09.000Z","uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8ec1cd601f002040d287e2466417f890804eeb","tid":164154,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟打算同女朋友係8月份去福岡加鹿兒島<br />\n如果係睇景同食野為主的話<br />\n去呢兩個地適唔適合呢<br />\n如果適合想問下咁嘅組合會唔會太怪？<br />\n同埋小弟都想浸溫泉<br />\n想問下果陣嘅天氣會唔會唔太適合<br />\n希望各位巴絲可以比下意見同解答下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf485ed938b1ab3def9f7535af1a87a8897979f","tid":164154,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T13:16:38.000Z","msg":"唔記左講添<br />\n小弟打算去一星期左右<br />\n7日6夜"},{"pid":"a0a1f015ff3904b4d62c5b63f6c83c7a6482ef72","tid":164154,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"落書局打下書釘先喇<br />\n再唔係goolgle下呢兩個地方有乜景點先<br />\n就咁好難答你架喎"},{"pid":"8f056f35157ff19d6137d2748f7001ac59cdc78c","tid":164154,"uid":50608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:35:39.000Z","msg":"我plan 10日9夜 都覺得唔夠時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6日5夜去福岡算數啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9664841a5784b147e1efaeaaa67fcd67e95fd44","tid":164154,"uid":50608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我plan 10日9夜 都覺得唔夠時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">7日6夜</span>去福岡算數啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"003429676e510facd6cf8034850cf7b5548f769f","tid":164154,"uid":14216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:38:48.000Z","msg":"8月浸溫泉 我包你落去唔夠一分鐘即上返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我舊年10月浸露天差啲中暑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08da80d0eb9fdaa273542094a662b342756eb970","tid":164154,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"30度浸温泉，超爽。<br />\n<br />\n利申：成日上水休息"},{"pid":"153f575a9825b58e4177e9825e60fb5522126e83","tid":164154,"uid":51602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:15:49.000Z","msg":"鹿児島 其實市中心同福岡好類似 <br />\n福岡博多中州天神繁華小小啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實2邊都有唔同周邊地方值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f60b9b79ee0e06934fc4c0fdb0499661929983","tid":164154,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鹿児島 其實市中心同福岡好類似 <br />\n福岡博多中州天神繁華小小啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實2邊都有唔同周邊地方值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同女朋友想去能克島同櫻島<br />\n其實我最怕無好野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb07d9f51ef744ecd140d62840fd89b337e3fcd","tid":164154,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:33:47.000Z","msg":"通常都係飛福岡玩北九州<br />\n飛鹿兒島玩南九州<br />\n淨去兩個城市咁奇怪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc854473385ee058a808fab0dbba435f5fdefcdc","tid":164154,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常都係飛福岡玩北九州<br />\n飛鹿兒島玩南九州<br />\n淨去兩個城市咁奇怪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚女朋友嫌麻煩,因為要拖gip周圍住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我諗緊好唔好淨係去其中一個城市"},{"pid":"857fb5aacc006b3ce2da4e2fa8dc2aa7cec24860","tid":164154,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"你會唔會去四國加山陰, 東京加北海道, 和歌山加北陸, 新潟加秋田? <br />\n唔係打卡分開啦"},{"pid":"7ad0878942edaa761aab15d9223817148d54153f","tid":164154,"uid":51602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>通常都係飛福岡玩北九州<br />\n飛鹿兒島玩南九州<br />\n淨去兩個城市咁奇怪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚女朋友嫌麻煩,因為要拖gip周圍住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我諗緊好唔好淨係去其中一個城市</blockquote><br />\n去晒都冇野<br />\n新幹線鹿児島本線好快<br />\n 但你唔去周邊其實冇意思"},{"pid":"55da8870d593f4d2317b4643eed263864e856d68","tid":164154,"uid":51602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:48:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>鹿児島 其實市中心同福岡好類似 <br />\n福岡博多中州天神繁華小小啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實2邊都有唔同周邊地方值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同女朋友想去能克島同櫻島<br />\n其實我最怕無好野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n能古島睇花 <br />\n桜島其實真係冇特別 遠睇個境就靚 <br />\n但去到唔揸車 既話係搽巴士遊一小部分 <br />\n好悶好傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6df1c4c9cab2f29ec4b09101abb500c657f290","tid":164154,"uid":51602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>鹿児島 其實市中心同福岡好類似 <br />\n福岡博多中州天神繁華小小啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實2邊都有唔同周邊地方值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同女朋友想去能克島同櫻島<br />\n其實我最怕無好野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n能古島睇花 <br />\n桜島其實真係冇特別 遠睇個境就靚 <br />\n但去到唔揸車 既話係坐巴士遊一小部分 <br />\n好悶好傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8d7a8476bc7b77ca23894857a40c260eb2cfc829","tid":164154,"uid":52679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"7日淨係北九州啦<br />\n買張5日pass <br />\n1日由布院<br />\n1日別府<br />\n1日熊本<br />\n2日長崎<br />\n淨返最後1~2日福岡買吓野"},{"pid":"959d5bd05fe4e61a758f3dee97c308b1dcb05201","tid":164154,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>通常都係飛福岡玩北九州<br />\n飛鹿兒島玩南九州<br />\n淨去兩個城市咁奇怪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚女朋友嫌麻煩,因為要拖gip周圍住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我諗緊好唔好淨係去其中一個城市</blockquote><br />\n去晒都冇野<br />\n新幹線鹿児島本線好快<br />\n 但你唔去周邊其實冇意思</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次去8日，北九州剩係去左福岡同長崎，然後去左鹿兒島四日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f7c1eace06fb88174bc57f5458c66cd5b066cb","tid":164154,"uid":51602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>通常都係飛福岡玩北九州<br />\n飛鹿兒島玩南九州<br />\n淨去兩個城市咁奇怪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚女朋友嫌麻煩,因為要拖gip周圍住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我諗緊好唔好淨係去其中一個城市</blockquote><br />\n去晒都冇野<br />\n新幹線鹿児島本線好快<br />\n 但你唔去周邊其實冇意思</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次去8日，北九州剩係去左福岡同長崎，然後去左鹿兒島四日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長崎我覺得有鬼城<br />\n但我又好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344ec33ee2afff24addb61753d4742874d076890","tid":164154,"uid":40842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T18:49:48.000Z","msg":"前排7日6夜北九州都覺得唔係好夠玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n福岡<br />\n別府<br />\n九州自然動物園<br />\n由布院<br />\n佐世保<br />\n豪斯登堡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔順路去唔到長崎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3856a8fe714e742e468d75f5a55019416b9ddec","tid":164154,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T18:54:38.000Z","msg":"訂左機票<br />\n6日5夜<br />\n計錯數,自膠<br />\n我同緊女朋友都傾緊係北九州玩好唔好<br />\n打算揀2個城市玩,想係福岡附近"},{"pid":"8c1c6489b9dba35275e262a1ab2923bebd0901a9","tid":164154,"uid":1370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T19:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訂左機票<br />\n6日5夜<br />\n計錯數,自膠<br />\n我同緊女朋友都傾緊係北九州玩好唔好<br />\n打算揀2個城市玩,想係福岡附近</blockquote><br />\n買北九州jr pass 每日去唔同城市行下食下野 夜晚返返福岡都唔錯"},{"pid":"6e1becb978bb13ee3d82b47bd1385e7be327381b","tid":164154,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>訂左機票<br />\n6日5夜<br />\n計錯數,自膠<br />\n我同緊女朋友都傾緊係北九州玩好唔好<br />\n打算揀2個城市玩,想係福岡附近</blockquote><br />\n買北九州jr pass 每日去唔同城市行下食下野 夜晚返返福岡都唔錯</blockquote><br />\n我果時都係咁<br />\n早上趕JR,去鹿兒島<br />\n晚上返<br />\n鹿兒島可以睇水族館,同埋D 博物館<br />\n不過D 地方分布得比較散<br />\n福岡我果震都係買買買 無咩特別野行"},{"pid":"3bfc5dc62e3d916515933fe6ac0d792188ced8ae","tid":164154,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你會唔會去四國加山陰, 東京加北海道, 和歌山加北陸, 新潟加秋田? <br />\n唔係打卡分開啦</blockquote><br />\n東京加北海道係好多人都會咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ecc2bb2d0e37b0196fea33f4dd9c85d80c8acb","tid":164154,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T10:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>訂左機票<br />\n6日5夜<br />\n計錯數,自膠<br />\n我同緊女朋友都傾緊係北九州玩好唔好<br />\n打算揀2個城市玩,想係福岡附近</blockquote><br />\n買北九州jr pass 每日去唔同城市行下食下野 夜晚返返福岡都唔錯</blockquote><br />\n我果時都係咁<br />\n早上趕JR,去鹿兒島<br />\n晚上返<br />\n鹿兒島可以睇水族館,同埋D 博物館<br />\n不過D 地方分布得比較散<br />\n福岡我果震都係買買買 無咩特別野行</blockquote><br />\n係咪買5日JR pass?<br />\n可能會留一日去鹿兒島嘅<br />\n咁巴打你當時係鹿兒島大約幾點走？"},{"pid":"882f9ee6847b852fdea401d3c9d28ef787e11e5b","tid":164154,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T10:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你會唔會去四國加山陰, 東京加北海道, 和歌山加北陸, 新潟加秋田? <br />\n唔係打卡分開啦</blockquote><br />\n東京加北海道係好多人都會咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n福岡落鹿兒島個半鐘新幹線，等如你上水出尖沙咀咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}